The '''Heritage Council''' was a council of [[Hapan]] nobles led by the [[Ducha]]s [[AlGray]] and [[Galney (Ducha of Terephon)|Galney]] who allied themselves with the [[Five Worlds]] during the [[Second Galactic Civil War]]. Their goal was to ensure the independence of the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]] from the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] by overthrowing [[Queen Mother]] [[Tenel Ka Djo|Tenel Ka]] and assassinating [[Chume'da]] [[Allana Djo Solo|Allana]]. To this end they hired the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Aurra Sing/Legends|Aurra Sing]] and [[Battle of Hapes (Second Galactic Civil War)|attacked]] the [[Hapan Royal Navy]] with [[Heritage Fleet|their fleet]]. The coup failed and most of the Heritage Council was captured or killed.

